sections.heading: Attachment; judgment for defendant; effect; return of property or proceeds
sections.text: If judgment is rendered in the action for the defendant, the attachment shall be discharged, and the property attached, or its proceeds, shall be returned to him.SourceR.S.1867, Code ยง 227, p. 431;R.S.1913, ยง 7761;C.S.1922, ยง
